body:
Game Of Codes - National Level Programming Contest.

  • Affiliated Mega Event: Techumen 2K16 - A National Level Tech Symposium.
  • Number of Signups in Techumen 2K16: 1560.
  • Role: Coordinator in Chief.
  • Event Date: 22th October 2016.
